## üßπ 4. ‡∏•‡∏î‡∏Ç‡∏ô‡∏≤‡∏î‡πÅ‡∏•‡∏∞ Optimize WSL2

‡πÄ‡∏°‡∏∑‡πà‡∏≠‡πÉ‡∏ä‡πâ‡πÑ‡∏õ‡∏ô‡∏≤‡∏ô ‡πÜ ‡πÑ‡∏ü‡∏•‡πå‡∏£‡∏∞‡∏ö‡∏ö‡∏Ç‡∏≠‡∏á WSL2 (`ext4.vhdx`) ‡∏à‡∏∞‡∏Ç‡∏¢‡∏≤‡∏¢‡∏à‡∏ô‡πÉ‡∏´‡∏ç‡πà‡πÄ‡∏Å‡∏¥‡∏ô‡∏à‡∏£‡∏¥‡∏á
‡πÉ‡∏´‡πâ‡∏•‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏á‡πÅ‡∏•‡∏∞‡∏ö‡∏µ‡∏ö‡∏≠‡∏±‡∏î‡∏Å‡∏•‡∏±‡∏ö‡∏î‡∏±‡∏á‡∏ô‡∏µ‡πâ

### üî∏ ‡∏†‡∏≤‡∏¢‡πÉ‡∏ô Ubuntu

```bash
sudo apt clean
sudo apt autoremove -y
mamba clean --all --yes
pip cache purge
rm -rf ~/.cache/*
```

### üî∏ ‡πÉ‡∏ô Windows PowerShell

```powershell
wsl --shutdown
```

‡∏ñ‡πâ‡∏≤‡πÉ‡∏ä‡πâ **Windows Home** ‡πÉ‡∏´‡πâ‡πÉ‡∏ä‡πâ `diskpart`:

```powershell
diskpart
select vdisk file="C:\Users\<username>\AppData\Local\Packages\<distro>\LocalState\ext4.vhdx"
attach vdisk readonly
compact vdisk
detach vdisk
exit
```

‡∏ñ‡πâ‡∏≤‡πÄ‡∏õ‡πá‡∏ô **Windows Pro** ‡πÉ‡∏ä‡πâ‡πÑ‡∏î‡πâ‡∏á‡πà‡∏≤‡∏¢‡∏Å‡∏ß‡πà‡∏≤‡∏ô‡∏µ‡πâ:

```powershell
Optimize-VHD -Path "C:\Users\<username>\AppData\Local\Packages\<distro>\LocalState\ext4.vhdx" -Mode Full
```

‡∏´‡∏•‡∏±‡∏á‡∏ó‡∏≥‡πÄ‡∏™‡∏£‡πá‡∏à ‡∏Ç‡∏ô‡∏≤‡∏î‡πÑ‡∏ü‡∏•‡πå `.vhdx` ‡∏à‡∏∞‡∏•‡∏î‡∏•‡∏á‡∏´‡∏•‡∏≤‡∏¢ GB ‡∏ó‡∏±‡∏ô‡∏ó‡∏µ üöÄ

